object.customQuery:
SELECT
    COALESCE(E.Policy_Key_Code, I.Policy_Key_Code) AS Policy_Key_Code,
    COALESCE(E.Policy_Key, I.Policy_Key) AS Policy_Key,
    COALESCE(E.Major_Peril_ID, I.Major_Peril_ID) AS Major_Peril_ID,
    COALESCE(E.Risk_State_ID, I.Risk_State_ID) AS Risk_State_ID,
    COALESCE(E.Account_Entered_Dt, I.Account_Entered_Dt) AS Account_Entered_Dt,
    E.Earned_Premium,
    E.Unearned_Premium,
    E.Commission_Amt,
    E.Taxes_Service_Charges,
    E.Written_Premium,
    I.Inforce_Policy_Key,
    I.Inforce_Premium,
    COALESCE(E.annual_statement_line, I.annual_statement_line) AS annual_statement_line,
    COALESCE(E.stateline, I.stateline) AS stateline,
	TGT.row_id,
	TGT.md5_hash_value
FROM
    dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw1 E
    FULL JOIN dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw2 I
        ON E.Policy_Key_Code        = I.Policy_Key_Code
       AND E.Policy_Key            = I.Policy_Key
       AND E.Major_Peril_ID        = I.Major_Peril_ID
       AND E.Risk_State_ID         = I.Risk_State_ID
       AND E.Account_Entered_Dt    = I.Account_Entered_Dt
	   AND COALESCE(E.Annual_Statement_Line,'NA') = COALESCE(I.Annual_Statement_Line,'NA')
	   AND COALESCE(E.Stateline,'NA')             = COALESCE(I.Stateline,'NA')
	   LEFT JOIN dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw3 TGT
        ON COALESCE(E.Policy_Key_Code, I.Policy_Key_Code) = TGT.Policy_Key_Code
       AND COALESCE(E.Policy_Key, I.Policy_Key)           = TGT.Policy_Key
       AND COALESCE(E.Major_Peril_ID, I.Major_Peril_ID)   = TGT.Major_Peril_ID
       AND COALESCE(E.Risk_State_ID, I.Risk_State_ID)     = TGT.Risk_State_ID
       AND COALESCE(E.Account_Entered_Dt, I.Account_Entered_Dt) = TGT.Account_Entered_Dt
	   AND COALESCE(E.annual_statement_line, I.annual_statement_line,'NA') = COALESCE(TGT.Annual_Statement_Line,'NA')
	   AND COALESCE(E.stateline, I.stateline,'NA') = COALESCE(TGT.Stateline,'NA')
	   AND COALESCE(I.Inforce_Policy_Key, 'NA') = COALESCE(TGT.Inforce_Policy_Key, 'NA')
WHERE
DATE_PART(year, COALESCE(E.Account_Entered_Dt, I.Account_Entered_Dt)) IN ('2020', '2021', '2022', '2023', '2024') AND
     (E.msgr_last_update_date >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views') OR
        I.msgr_last_update_date >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views'))

--E.Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date))

 --or I.Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date))
